            I am very grateful to the noble Baroness for her response. I shall read what she has said very carefully in <span class="italic">Hansard</span>. I do not know whether we shall bring the provision back on Report, but at this stage I thank the noble Baroness for that full explanation. For now, I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
