      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-02200'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040512_GCR_318' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The aim of the amendments is to tease out whether replacing divorce with a right to end a partnership on request would be acceptable to the Government. I do
        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_172gc' title='Col. 172GC &mdash; HL Deb 12 May 2004 vol 661 c172GC' name='column_172gc' href='#column_172gc' rel='bookmark'>172GC</a>
